<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend_Rest_Client (version 1.5.2) doesn't support CDATA in it's result, I
just made a small change in the code so it works but was wondering if this
might be fixed already or will be in the future?</p>

<p>The change: Add the LIBXML_NOCDATA param to the simplexml_load_string()
function in \Rest\Client\Result.php.</p>

